  <span id="freeText15634098814296208773" style="display:none">For an alternate history filled with wizards and vampires, the Shakespearean self-seriousness of this book is wild.<br /><br />I'm honestly sad this isn't a series, because I really want to see other parts of this universe where the Byzantine empire flourished, learn more about its magic and discover what other historical figures could have been brought in.</span>
