      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1791898-the-dragon-waiting">Quotes from The Dragon Waiting</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Then the syncretist Ficino, sitting hunched with Lorenzo standing at his side, put all the ideas together, along with Lorenzo's new song: chariots blazing between the worlds as gods fought rebel gods, the destruction of a city -- a planet? -- by fire, beasts beyond imagining both to terrify and befriend the heroes.<br /><br />"It needs a title," Signorina Scala said.<br /><br />Pulci had his mouth open, but Ficino beat him to the pun.<br /><br />"It shall be dedicated to Isis and Mars," he said, "and we will call it <i>Stella Martis</i>.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/580376-then-the-syncretist-ficino-sitting-hunched-with-lorenzo-standing-at">3 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
